data.title: Dallon Weekes
data.meta_description: Dallon James Weekes (born May 4, 1981) is an American singer, songwriter, musician, and record producer. He was a member of Panic! at the Disco from 2009 to 2017, performing in the band as a bassist, keyboardist, and backing vocalist.
